Package com.lucaslouca.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LLTownMap
    The LLTownMap interface represents a map that stores towns using a LLDirectedGraph underneath.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LLDirectedGraph<T>
    Class representing a generic directed graph.
    LLPropertyFactory
    Class loading and holding the contents of com.lucaslouca.trains.properties.
    LLTownMapImpl
    The LLTownMapImpl class implements the LLTownMap interface.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    LLDirectedGraph.NodeNotReachableException
    Exception that is thrown when a node in the graph is not reachable.
    LLTownMapImpl.NoSuchRouteException
    Exception that is thrown when a provided route is not valid because a town or road to that town does not exist.
